headline: Q2 Rundown: CarMax (NYSE:KMX) Vs Other Vehicle Retailer Stocks
summary: As the Q2 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the vehicle retailer industry, including CarMax (NYSE:KMX) and its peers.
